snippet.title: Werewolf Tycoon Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the Big Bad Wolf of Werewolf Park in this werewolf stealth simulation game. Happy munching! 

Werewolf Tycoon is available for free:

Android Google Play - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=uk.co.joecreates.werewolftycoon
Amazon Kindle - http://www.amazon.com/Joe-Williamson-Werewolf-Tycoon/dp/B00QD0MTLE
Apple App Store - http://appstore.com/werewolftycoon

Like - https://www.facebook.com/WerewolfTycoon
